(31,	1,	'2015-06-25 02:53:41',	'2015-06-25 02:53:41',	'<p> \r\nUpload the photo and choose one of the payment below.<br>\r\nFile Upload **2mb max filesize</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[file file-01 limit:2000000 filetypes:png|jpg|jpeg]</p>\r\n<p class=\"hide\">[file file-02 limit:2000000 filetypes:png|jpg|jpeg]<a class=\"del_file\" href=\"#\">del</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"hide\">[file file-03 limit:2000000 filetypes:png|jpg|jpeg]<a class=\"del_file\" href=\"#\">del</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"hide\">[file file-04 limit:2000000 filetypes:png|jpg|jpeg]<a class=\"del_file\" href=\"#\">del</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"hide\">[file file-05 limit:2000000 filetypes:png|jpg|jpeg]<a class=\"del_file\" href=\"#\">del</a></p>\r\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"add_file\">Add file</a>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p> Select Job Payment <br />\r\n[select* menu-paypal \"Basic Service 1 - $3 NZD\" \"Basic Service 2 - $5 NZD\" \"Basic Service 3 - $10 NZD\"]\r\n</p> \r\n\r\n<p>Your Email (required)<br />\r\n    [email* your-email] </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Job Details (required)<br />\r\n    [textarea your-message] </p>\r\n\r\n<p>[submit \"Send\"]</p>\nRequest for a Job\n<paolomanarang@gmail.com>\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\nA Job Request has been Posted for you chanman\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\nRequest Detail Payment\r\n[menu-paypal]\r\n--\r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on  (http://localhost/chano/site)\npaolomanarang@gmail.com\nReply-To: [your-email]\n[file-01][file-02][file-03][file-04][file-05]\n\n\n\n[your-subject]\n<paolomanarang@gmail.com>\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n--\r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on  (http://localhost/chano/site)\n[your-email]\nReply-To: paolomanarang@gmail.com\n\n\n\nYour message was sent successfully. Thanks.\nFailed to send your message. Please try later or contact the administrator by another method.\nValidation errors occurred. Please confirm the fields and submit it again.\nFailed to send your message. Please try later or contact the administrator by another method.\nPlease accept the terms to proceed.\nPlease fill in the required field.\nThis input is too long.\nThis input is too short.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nNumber format seems invalid.\nThis number is too small.\nThis number is too large.\nEmail address seems invalid.\nURL seems invalid.\nTelephone number seems invalid.\nYour answer is not correct.\nDate format seems invalid.\nThis date is too early.\nThis date is too late.\nFailed to upload file.\nThis file type is not allowed.\nThis file is too large.\nFailed to upload file. Error occurred.',	'Contact form 1',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'contact-form-1',	'',	'',	'2015-07-07 07:55:02',	'2015-07-07 07:55:02',	'',	0,	'http://localhost/chano/site/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=31',	0,	'wpcf7_contact_form',	'',	0),
